portsIn.value: During the Corona lockdown, in early 2020, I was thinking of things that I could really enjoy. at that moment I explored and learned about music and started to produce music though I have no background in art or music. I focus towards ambient music and sound scape. In summer 2021, I gained interest on Audio-Visual experience. Due pandemic and restriction, I'm thinking to make it accessible for everyone by creating this experience on website.
